ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If the student wants to learn and implement practical algorithms in data mining, I won't recommend; if s/he wants to learn more math, I highly recommend.
I will recommend it to those who has an interest in the application of math in data mining, rather than in data mining topics.
An excellent introductory course. Definitely take this if you want to brush up on linear algebra!Yes, I would recommend this course, because it has helped me immensely.
yes. It can help student design data mining task using the principle instead of heuristic.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It helps me with understanding the base of data mining, and C programming language.
